{"tid":2071197,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉建源稱閱讀計劃書單限制選擇　局方指專業角度推介","createTime":"2020-06-19T15:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T16:11:09.000Z","uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1b9da725614fac5eecf6389ccc7522d1f75efc","tid":2071197,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:39:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533076-20200619.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533076-20200619.htm&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w1xDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=70b60c25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533076-20200619.htm&h=8b4aabdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533076-20200619.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n教育界立法會議員葉建源說，教育局昨日宣布推出的暑期閱讀贈閱計劃，推行過急，書單限制學生閱讀選擇，有利益輸送之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n葉建源說，教育局昨日才發出有關通知，要求學校下星期三選好書，進行報價及採購，7月暑假前便要向學生派發書籍，令到原本要處理大量工作的學校要急於做好決定，不少學校的圖書館主任質疑為何計劃推行如此急促。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，可供選擇的書籍當中超過7成，即500多本來自中資機構的聯合集團，令人質疑有利益輸送問題，要求教育局公開交代此計劃的細節，並為學校提供彈性時間安排。"},{"pid":"f6e29b604e679c5994124490b4f1f581532c925e","tid":2071197,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:51:16.000Z","msg":"借個位 立會事實處 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2070889/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2070889/page/1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec9f6348586228296722f1c619b6f99c1e97646","tid":2071197,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"專業角度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cedb729c48cf89335e0064d3488a779ac5b4c1a","tid":2071197,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:58:54.000Z","ms